
Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [06/30/2024]

Introduction
Thank you for using Japan Pop from LuTri Games. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Game. Please read this privacy policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this privacy policy, please do not access the Game.
Information Collection

Personal Information:
We do not collect any personal information that identifies you as an individual and no account or login is required to play this game.
Non-Personal Information:
We collect non-personal information that does not directly identify you. This includes:
•	Game settings
•	Round progress
•	In-game preferences

Local Storage:
All data related to your game settings and progress is stored locally on your Android device. We do not store any game-related data on our servers.

Third-Party Services

AdMob:
The Game uses AdMob for in-game advertisements. AdMob may collect and use data according to their privacy policy. For more information, please visit AdMob Privacy Policy.

Unity Purchase (IAP):
The Game uses Unity's In-App Purchase (IAP) service for handling transactions. Unity may collect data necessary for processing these transactions according to their privacy policy. For more information, please visit Unity Privacy Policy.
Advertisements and Purchases
The Game contains advertisements and offers in-app purchases. However, it is a free game and there is no obligation for users to pay for any features or content. All core functionalities of the Game are available without any payment. In-app purchases are optional and are designed to enhance the user experience.

Children’s Privacy
Although the Game is not specifically targeted at children, it may be played by users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, know that we do not store personal information, feel free to contact us for more details.

Music Credits
All background music featured in this application is credited to FREE BGM DOVA-SYNDROME. The songs used in the Game are created by しゃろうのBGM and are used in accordance with the terms of usage stipulated by DOVA-SYNDROME. This ensures compliance with licensing requirements and respects the intellectual property of the music creators. Users are encouraged to explore further compositions by しゃろうのBGM on platforms such as YouTube to discover additional works by the artist.

Data Security
We prioritize the security of your data. All locally stored data is protected by the security mechanisms provided by the Android operating system. However, please be aware that no method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Distribution and Commercialization
This game is intended for personal use only. It should not be distributed, shared, or commercialized by unauthorized individuals or entities. Any unauthorized distribution or commercialization of this game is prohibited and may result in legal action.

App Usage and Resource Consumption
Please note that the Japan Pop app may utilize battery, memory, and mobile data while in use. The app displays advertisements that may require internet connectivity, which can consume mobile data. Users are advised to monitor their device's battery and data usage accordingly.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at lutri.faq.games@outlook.com
